name: Back To The Bitcoin
description:
You shouldn’t buy the dip right now, but the Doc will bring you with time machine to 2010 and buy a lot of bitcoin, it's time back to the bitcoin,  with a wallet full of Bitcoin.   
Conceptual art to make NFT, using existing pictures on the internet and recreate with a basic app and colour black and white as a meme comic, and let the picture talk about crypto.
